rComments: I LOVED this class! She is by far my favorite professor on campus! The stuff we learned in class, I actually applied to my marketing internship AND she is super helpful with your career search!

If you're wearing a Gucci suit, you're in. You must be "fabulous" for her to pay any attention to you. Terrible favoritism. Decent lecturer. Funny, but misleading on first day. Go to class with a D&B purse and you're in.
Great professor.  Doesn't require a textbook.  She knows her stuff and is very engaging!  Class - BADM 523
Knowledgable professor, but does not teach class very well. Always reads off power point slides and gives you way too much work for 3 credit hours.
